Interface IFormulaInSecurity

All Known Subinterfaces:
IFormulaSecurityLoad
All Known Implementing Classes:
Security
public interface IFormulaInSecurity
Projection interface for derived-security price formulas.

Provides mapping from a link securitycurrency to its formula for price calculation, with an indicator whether the formula is applied to calculate the price.
